Interface ServiceConnector.Callback<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the data type returned by the method call
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EmployeeConnector.EmployeeCallback, MerchantConnector.MerchantCallback, PrinterConnector.PrinterCallback, ReceiptRegistrationConnector.ReceiptRegistrationCallback, ServiceCallback, TenderConnector.TenderCallback
    Enclosing class:
    ServiceConnector<S extends IInterface>

    public static interface ServiceConnector.Callback<T>
    Responds to the results of a call to a ServiceConnector method. All the callback methods are executed on the main thread.
